中间色邻近色调的 8 号色；"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"保留未分段的色带，便于用户自由分段取数。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*VLGeTo8a2e0AAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","alt":"image.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":" 邻近色色板（部分）**"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"发散色色板","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%E5%8F%91%E6%95%A3%E8%89%B2%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF","ariaLabel":"发散色色板 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"发散色色板"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定义"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 也称对比色渐变色板，一般是两种互补色（也可以是对比色）去展现数据从一个负向值到 0 点再到正向值的连续变化区间，显示相对立的两个值的大小关系。数据范围的两端同等强调中间值和极值，以表示断点(如零变化或平均值)周围与数据中特定有意义的中间值之间的差异。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"取色指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 关键断点应该采用中性颜色及与背景色对比度低，如浅灰色，端点应该采用和背景色对比度高的饱和颜色。一般来说是对称的，临界断点可以是平均值、中间值或零变化值。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"取色方法"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ol","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"选取分类色板中的对比色或互补色，其中 7 号色起始色和结束色，4 号色为过渡色，灰阶色的 1 号色作为中间色，在 CIELab 色彩空间下生成渐变色；"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"暗色色板同理，其中 8 号色起始色和结束色，5 号色为过渡色，灰阶色的 2 号色作为中间色；"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"保留未分段的色带，便于用户自由分段取数。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*Yx7-Rpm3ORwAAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","alt":"image.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":" 发散色板（部分）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"语义色板","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%E8%AF%AD%E4%B9%89%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF","ariaLabel":"语义色板 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"语义色板"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"定义"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 色彩在可视化中的使用，不仅是数据信息传递的可视化通道，同时也是更深一层的文化故事的载体，用于表达意义或情感。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"取色指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 重视用色习惯，遵循相关标准，色彩也不是都能寓意的，相当一部分图表色彩选择和感情因素无关，而是按照某种习惯来设定色彩，即所谓约定俗成，有的甚至形成来规范。 "},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*O7j0QIOATF0AAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","alt":"image.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":" 语义色板（部分）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"更多色板介绍，详见 "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"../language/palette"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AntV 色板"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{"id":"设计-tips","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1-tips","ariaLabel":"设计 tips permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1