{"type":"text","value":"统计学概念,又称连续变量。指在一定区间内可以任意取值、数值是连续不断的、相邻两个数值可作无限分割(即可取无限个数值)的数据。 "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"断点："}]},{"type":"text","value":"文中主要指数据集的中心值或参考值，例如零变化或平均值。 "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"端点："}]},{"type":"text","value":"文中主要指数据集极端值，例如最大最小值。 "},{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"语义："}]},{"type":"text","value":"文中主要指色彩心理学中色彩在客观上对人们对一种刺激和象征，它在主观上又是一种反应和行为。包含从知觉、感情而到记忆、思想、意志、象征等与色彩的因果关系。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*JxX5RIoxGO8AAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","alt":"image.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当需要用颜色作为视觉通道时，数据性质可作为参考因素，选用色板的步骤大致如下图： "},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"src":"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_a8a5bf/afts/img/A*McaSTIbSrigAAAAAAAAAAAAAARQnAQ","alt":"image.png"},"children":[]}]}],"data":{"quirksMode":false}},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/graph/#%E5%9B%BE%E6%9E%84%E6%88%90%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\">图构成元素</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/graph/#%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%88node%EF%BC%89\">节点（Node）</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/graph/#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\">定义</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/graph/#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81\">常见形态</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/graph/#%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\">交互样式</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/graph/#%E8%BE%B9%EF%BC%88edge%EF%BC%89\">边（Edge）</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/graph/graph/#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89-1\